{"tid":749451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★【校園至抵價】$12000請水電牌校工","createTime":"2018-07-20T04:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T11:13:04.000Z","uid":19454,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"71f1d88306e7d1f3db221fd5d5601e68c9a14a16","tid":749451,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T04:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://19ga.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/4364578-1024x770.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F19ga.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F4364578-1024x770.png&h=3ad326b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，你冇睇錯，呢個係元朗區某中學的招聘廣告，聘請「全職維修技工兼校工」及「全職校工」，一星期返6日，講到明「持水電牌優先」、「懂園藝優先」，再睇落去，捽吓對眼，以為自己睇錯，寫住「月薪︰港幣$12,475起（視乎工作經驗而定）」。<br />\n<br />\n廣告一出，即刻引來熱議。幾乎一面倒聲音話︰「返足6日，又要水電牌，酒店同商場都已經$16,000起跳，有大部分甚至去到$20,000起。」亦有網民話︰「求其做份物管都至少$15,500，點解要拎住水電牌逗一份可恥的人工?」<br />\n<br />\n再睇吓職責內容，要負責校園保養及維修、清潔及搬運等，萬二蚊全包咁濟，認真抵請。<br />\n<br />\n有呢個Quali而肯入去做的，得一個原因︰想小朋友入呢間學校搏有分加，完。<br />\n<br />\n來源︰盡在元朗facebook<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://heawork.19ga.hk/2018071133367/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fheawork.19ga.hk%2F2018071133367%2F&d=ZswPy%2BAChJBw01jT6W8w0%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=a8271397\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://heawork.19ga.hk/2018071133367/</a>"},{"pid":"8aea9f0ccfb5083ccdcf618f86f2509f543a8934","tid":749451,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T04:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/011226_eba6400fe2bfe149f90560d62bc89cd4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F011226_eba6400fe2bfe149f90560d62bc89cd4.png&h=d3057e31&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5118a1e0f7d75876b31baa74f6e37101deb1ea6a","tid":749451,"uid":44333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T04:45:44.000Z","msg":"有得入女廁"},{"pid":"701ec1e50ff624b738419c47ae6ff1f6279b413c","tid":749451,"u